#{{cattag|Physics}}: In [[special relativity]], the pattern describing the [[temporal]] [[evolution]] of a flash of [[light]] in [[Minkowski spacetime]]. This is [[modeled]] in 3-space using the two [[horizontal]] [[axes]] as [[spatial]] [[dimension]]s, while the [[vertical]] axis is [[time]].